{"tid":1026142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國前乒乓國手鄧亞萍被指兒子是法國籍     鄧亞萍曬護照澄清","createTime":"2019-02-18T01:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T10:17:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":70,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"549c5b385e14cb0773dce1290c69b6dd899eab8c","tid":1026142,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/sports/page/800/2019/02/17/phpY1d1jp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fsports%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F02%2F17%2FphpY1d1jp.jpg&h=7beb0721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾拿下4面奧運金牌、並在世界桌壇連續8年稱霸的中國「桌球女皇」鄧亞萍，日前因在法國出生12歲兒子的國籍問題，躍上新聞版面，而今她突在微博PO出自己和兒子的中國護照發表聲明，表示「兩人一直都是中國籍」，再度引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n根據中媒報導，「桌球女皇」鄧亞萍16歲首次參加世桌賽就奪得女雙冠軍， 1992年巴塞隆納奧運，一鳴驚人，奪得女子單、雙打兩面金牌，1996年的亞特蘭大奧運，又成功複製4年前的奇蹟，成為中國奧運歷史上第一個奪得四枚奧運金牌的人。<br />\n<br />\n直到1998年9月正式宣布退役，鄧亞萍在14年的運動生涯中，共拿到18個世界冠軍，她在桌壇排名連續8年保持世界第一，是桌球排名史上「世界第一」時間最長的女性運動員。<br />\n<br />\n而鄧亞萍在退役後出國留學，和同是桌球選手的丈夫林志剛低調結婚，去年年底兒子林瀚銘曝光，繼承父母優良基因，12歲就入選北京桌球二隊，不過當時卻被傳出，出生在法國的林瀚銘使用的是法國國籍，而非中國，讓鄧亞萍挨轟是在替「法國人培養球員」。<br />\n<br />\n而鄧亞萍今將前往摩納哥參加勞倫斯世界體育獎（Laureus World Sports Awards）頒獎典禮，她突然在社交媒體發文，並附上二人的中國及法國的護照照片，澄清自己和兒子的國籍問題，指出「我和兒子林瀚銘一直以來都是中國籍，雖然他出生在法國，但一出生就拿了中國護照。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過，鄧亞萍的「澄清」卻似乎未能讓完全安撫中國網友。仍有中國網友認為，林翰銘生於法國，已擁有法國居留權（綠卡），將來也還是可以申請法國國籍。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2701732\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2701732&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgKVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=9c4b6700\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2701732&h=304ee195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2701732</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3901/3901900.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3901%2F3901900.jpg&h=5d796c68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190217/1380153.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190217%2F1380153.htm&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgKVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=bd3a3d2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190217/1380153.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5406b65f140613171cd10858663ad437696c3e8e","tid":1026142,"uid":36901,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:23:48.000Z","msg":"黑頭髮<br />\n即係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04c242b1fe22b8519ff27f5da8f7782406a417c","tid":1026142,"uid":40723,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:25:54.000Z","msg":"鎖國啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9feb465f7c67a61fe2d5c593e18a3eea022c744d","tid":1026142,"uid":90704,"like":137,"dislike":0,"score":137,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:29:48.000Z","msg":"牙萍個仔有國籍問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n領導全家外國籍喎"},{"pid":"712e9f795fcb7f730b058d7a025b2e3d6131c974","tid":1026142,"uid":5715,"like":110,"dislike":5,"score":105,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:31:05.000Z","msg":"有中國護照唔代表無外國籍架喎"},{"pid":"0cd23a2b705174a270a4b8045ce2aebcc98eae70","tid":1026142,"uid":53026,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:37:15.000Z","msg":"好人好姐點解去外國生仔？"},{"pid":"20f761ca6aba3218170d4b654fb44daac848f06c","tid":1026142,"uid":20170,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:54:42.000Z","msg":"心底話：我做唔到法國人 走唔出鬼國 卯以你都要一齊做鬼國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f5b22cd8baa100983e692929d3d9c67123a55b","tid":1026142,"uid":20170,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>心底話：我做唔到法國人 走唔出鬼國 所以你都要一齊做鬼國人<img src=\"